            <title>[LU-3805] Test failure on test suite conf-sanity, subtest test_32a</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3805</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Oleg Drokin &amp;lt;green@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b24de72a-09e6-11e3-b8ef-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/b24de72a-09e6-11e3-b8ef-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_32a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CMD: client-20-ib /usr/sbin/lctl conf_param t32fs-OST0000.osc.max_dirty_mb=15&lt;br/&gt;
client-20-ib: error: conf_param: File exists&lt;br/&gt;
 conf-sanity test_32a: @@@@@@ FAIL: Setting &quot;max_dirty_mb&quot; &lt;br/&gt;
test_32a failed with 2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: conf-sanity 32a&lt;/p&gt;</description>
